version_description: This song is in the key of B
My version is different because I think it's more accurate and it's easier to read and it's got everything you need in the song. Chords, Inro, Solo, etc. And the chords are in the right places.
This song is in the Key of B
3 chords which can be easily transposed for capo -- the chords are centered around the solo guitar line, hence the slightly varied placement throughout the song.
This song is in the Key of D
It is exactly what Luke plays in the video that they have up on their YouTube channel.
